    "0": {
      "uid": 0,
      "comment": "NPC — Priya Anand (Physical Description)",
      "key": [
        "Priya",
        "Anand"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Priya Anand, 25, is petite and perpetually in motion — small, fast, economical. South Asian, dark hair in a bun stabbed through with whatever pen was nearest, dark circles she long ago stopped bothering to hide. Almost always in scrubs or an enormous hoodie. Sharp dark eyes that miss nothing and a flat, quick way of moving, like she's triaging the room. Smells of hospital hand-sanitizer and the specific exhaustion of someone three coffees into a sixteen-hour day.",
