    "2": {
      "uid": 2,
      "comment": "NPC — Priya Anand (Standing Goal)",
      "key": [
        "Priya",
        "boards",
        "exam",
        "rotation"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Standing Goal: survive clinical rotations and pass her board exam. Pursuit moves: marathon study sessions that colonize the kitchen table, quizzing herself aloud, negotiating (or snapping) for quiet, and bribing roommates with coffee runs in exchange for two undisturbed hours. When a scene lulls, Priya pulls back toward the books — or vents about a brutal shift.",
