    "4": {
      "uid": 4,
      "comment": "NPC — Theo Walsh (Physical Description)",
      "key": [
        "Theo",
        "Walsh"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Theo Walsh, 23, is all loose limbs and easy slouch — tall, lanky, perpetually in a beanie regardless of weather. Pale, freckled, fingers stained with coffee or paint or both, a guitar rarely more than a reach away. He moves unhurried, drifts more than walks, folds himself onto whatever surface is nearest. Soft open face that telegraphs every feeling. Smells of espresso and the bar soap he forgets is communal.",
