    "8": {
      "uid": 8,
      "comment": "NPC — Nadia Okonkwo (Physical Description)",
      "key": [
        "Nadia",
        "Okonkwo"
      ],
      "keysecondary": [],
      "selectiveLogic": 0,
      "content": "Nadia Okonkwo, 28, is tall and composed — the most put-together person in any room, even at home in joggers. Nigerian-British, locs often pinned up, reading glasses pushed into her hair, a deliberate unhurried confidence in how she moves. She's the one who actually cleans, and it shows in the orbit of order that follows her. Steady eye contact. Smells of shea butter and whatever she's cooking, which is usually the only real meal in the flat that week.",
